snippet.title: Robbie Swifthand and the Orb of Mysteries - DEMO
snippet.description:
Download and play our demo for free at Gamejolt ! 
Link: http://gamejolt.com/games/RobbieSwifthand/272862

Want to support us ?

Leave a like on our facebook page : https://www.facebook.com/PixelReign/
Follow us on instagram : https://www.instagram.com/pixelreign/
Follow us on twitter : https://twitter.com/PixelReign

And if you really liked our game please share it with a friend !

We sincerely hope you enjoy the game and that you follow our progress, feedback is always welcome as well as bug reports (if you find any bugs or issues please let us know via our facebook page or via e-mail at pxlreign@gmail.com).

Thank you for reading through all this text, we really appreciate it ! Have fun !
